## Backlinks

<% if resource.backlinks.any? -%>
<% resource.backlinks.each do |r| -%>
<% if r.respond_to?(:created_by_id) && blocked_user_ids.include?(r.created_by_id) -%>
* *[Link from a user you have blocked]*
<% else -%>
* <%= r.class.name %>: [<%= r.respond_to?(:title) ? r.title : "#{r.class.name} #{r.truncated_id}" %>](<%= r.path %>)
<% end -%>
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
No backlinks yet.
<% end -%>
